00:12:08,815 --> 00:12:10,033
-Hello?

110
00:12:10,077 --> 00:12:11,818
-Cufe. What's up?

111
00:12:11,861 --> 00:12:14,255
What the fuck you doing home?

112
00:12:14,298 --> 00:12:15,909
We got work to do.

113
00:12:15,952 --> 00:12:17,693
-I'm digging a fricking grave,
man.

114
00:12:17,737 --> 00:12:21,218
-Hey, I didn't put your father
