115
00:12:21,262 --> 00:12:22,524
Come on, man.

116
00:12:22,567 --> 00:12:24,569
I need you to get some weights.

117
00:12:24,613 --> 00:12:25,701
-Weights?

118
00:12:25,745 --> 00:12:27,137
How much?

119
00:12:27,181 --> 00:12:29,705
-Well, how much do you think
he weighed?

120
00:12:29,749 --> 00:12:33,100
-I don't know ...
150 pounds maybe?

121
00:12:33,143 --> 00:12:34,536
-Yeah, I got an idea.

122
00:12:34,579 --> 00:12:37,104
And don't fuck around, either.
Come on.

123
00:12:37,147 --> 00:12:39,193
-I'm not, man.
And where the hell are you?

124
00:12:39,236 --> 00:12:40,977
You said you were gonna
come down and help me out.

125
00:12:41,021 --> 00:12:42,326
-Yeah.

126
00:12:42,370 --> 00:12:44,633
-♪ Bring your warriors
from the past ♪

127
00:12:44,676 --> 00:12:48,898
-♪ micco rebel from the sun

128
00:12:48,942 --> 00:12:53,685
♪ bring your warriors
from the past ♪

129
00:12:53,729 --> 00:12:57,864
♪ micco rebel from the sun

130
00:12:57,907 --> 00:12:59,648
♪ bring your warriors...

131
00:12:59,691 --> 00:13:00,997
-Hi, Larry.

132
00:13:01,041 --> 00:13:02,694
