all day.

147
00:13:39,209 --> 00:13:40,732
-All right, then.

148
00:13:40,776 --> 00:13:43,300
-♪ Yo, this is dedicated
to the west coast ♪

149
00:13:43,344 --> 00:13:45,520
♪ this is dedicated
to the midwest ♪

150
00:13:45,563 --> 00:13:47,914
♪ this is dedicated
to the reservation ♪

151
00:13:47,957 --> 00:13:49,916
♪ this is dedicated
to the rest ♪

152
00:13:49,959 --> 00:13:52,005
[ Singing in native language ]

153
00:13:58,838 --> 00:14:00,100
-Hey.

154
00:14:00,143 --> 00:14:02,667
Sonny brought
your dad's coffin in.

155
00:14:02,711 --> 00:14:04,452
Man, he's a crazy fucker.

156
00:14:04,495 --> 00:14:06,410
Guy cracks me up.

157
00:14:06,454 --> 00:14:09,152
