249
00:19:44,139 --> 00:19:45,227
-Cufe.

250
00:19:45,271 --> 00:19:47,925
-Where was he?
-In his chair.

251
00:19:55,629 --> 00:19:57,761
-I can't believe
he's fucking dead.

252
00:19:57,805 --> 00:19:59,241
-Can we not talk about this?

253
00:19:59,285 --> 00:20:00,764
-Mom, we just had his funeral.

254
00:20:00,808 --> 00:20:02,679
How can we not talk about him?

255
00:20:02,723 --> 00:20:04,115
-It's depressing.

256
00:20:04,159 --> 00:20:05,856
-Well, yeah.
How'd you think it'd be?

257
00:20:07,510 --> 00:20:10,252
-[ Sighs ]

258
00:20:10,296 --> 00:20:12,123
So, you still have that job?

259
00:20:12,167 --> 00:20:15,039
-[ Scoffs ] Shit.

260
00:20:15,083 --> 00:20:16,258
Forget it.

261
00:20:16,302 --> 00:20:19,087
-Fine.
-Fine.

262
00:20:19,130 --> 00:20:20,741
I knew this would be
a pain in the ass.

263
00:20:20,784 --> 00:20:23,004
-Quit your cussing.
It's your daddy's funeral.

264
00:20:23,047 --> 00:20:24,745
-Fuck you.

265
00:20:24,788 --> 00:20:26,790
-Fuck you!

266
00:20:30,838 --> 00:20:33,406
-I would have come earlier...
But work.

267
00:20:33,449 --> 00:20:34,755
